Senior Care Organizer Workshop||<p>This 2 session interactive workshop is designed to help those who are currently facing (or preparing to face) parent care issues, as well as those who may want to make plans for themselves or their parents, even though they are healthy now.</p>
<p>You'll receive a wealth of parent care information and resources, as well as the opportunity to ask questions. Cost is $25 per participant. Led by Contact Claudia Rumwell, RN. Want to know more? <a href="http://www.pcctoday.com/life-learning/personal-life-classes/senior-care-organizer-workshop/">click here to register</a>.</p>